vega.hipe.pds

Class PDSImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • SimpleImage
      • vega.hipe.pds.PDSImage

  • public class PDSImage
extends SimpleImage
    Class that stores an image read in Planetary Data Science format. As it inherit from SimpleImage it can be handle by Hipe and save as FITS

        minimumLongitude - Longitude of the left upper corner of the rectangle
        maximumLatitude - Latitude of the right down corner of the rectangle
        maximumLongitude - Longitude of the right down corner of the rectangle
        Returns:
        Throws:
        InvalidValueException - If any of the corners are outside the current picture

      • descalate

        public PDSImage descalate(float factor)
                   throws InvalidValueException
        Reduce the scale of this picture by a factor. 1.0 is the same scale of this picture. 0.0 is a no picture
        Parameters:
        factor - a float value between 0 and 1
        Returns:
        The escalated image
        Throws:
        InvalidValueException - if the factor is greater than 1 or less than 0
